meta.description: Temporary fork of PuLP offering support for Python 3 while retaining compatibility with Python 2. PuLP is an LP modeler that can generate MPS or LPfiles and call GLPK, COIN CLP/CBC, CPLEX, and GUROBI to solve linear problems
